%% Appointment Status Lifecycle
flowchart LR
  Created{{created}} --> Upcoming["upcoming (auto-confirmed)"]
  Upcoming -. time passes IST .-> Due["due (frontend-only)"]
  Upcoming -->|PATCH status| Cons["in_consultation"]
  Cons --> Treat["in_treatment"]
  Treat --> Done["completed"]
  Upcoming -->|cancel + WhatsApp| Cancel["cancelled"]
  Cons --> Cancel
